title: She Has Skeletons And Bodies
itunes:title: She Has Skeletons And Bodies
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I met my wife on an online dating site two years ago. All of the things she wanted in a mate matched mine to a tee. She had been married before and I had been engaged but I had called off my wedding in the nick of time. I shared my horrible experience with my wife and I told her that my ex had a past that I was unaware of and her own family was the one to tell me about her......................
